{"tid":761331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國外相侯俊偉關注香港一國兩制受損","createTime":"2018-07-30T09:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T10:34:37.000Z","uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b4baa286fa3e9b5fee0a3c563a29ff6255277023","tid":761331,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T09:55:08.000Z","msg":"侯俊偉關注香港一國兩制受損 更新：2018/07/30 17:05<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/531816/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E4%BE%AF%E4%BF%8A%E5%81%89%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A9%E5%88%B6%E5%8F%97%E6%90%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F531816%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E4%25BE%25AF%25E4%25BF%258A%25E5%2581%2589%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%258F%2597%25E6%2590%258D&d=FN1IPIf6A5MM2oCOz3Xkky7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=ec0e5a0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F531816%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E4%25BE%25AF%25E4%25BF%258A%25E5%2581%2589%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%258F%2597%25E6%2590%258D&h=bcf74b58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/531816/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E4%BE%AF%E4%BF%8A%E5%81%89%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A9%E5%88%B6%E5%8F%97%E6%90%8D</a><br />\n<br />\n英國外相侯俊偉訪華與外長王毅會面，提到關注香港事務，王毅指香港問題是中國內政，不容許別國干預。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">英國外相侯俊偉稱，與外長王毅會談期間，討論過人權等問題，雙方有很大分歧，又指二人討論到香港人權狀況。 </span><br />\n<br />\n王毅表示，香港回歸後，香港事務就是中國內政，中方不歡迎，也不會允許別國干涉內部事務，他強調中國當然繼續奉行一國兩制，依法處理香港事務，堅持一國兩制，港人治港、高度自治的原則和方針，不會有任何變化。<br />\n<br />\n香港在一國兩制方針指引下，不斷保持發展、繁榮和穩定，他又指香港競爭力、透明度和開放度，繼續在世上名列前茅，反映一國兩制成功實踐，相信特區政府會本著《基本法》處理好香港事務，中央政府會依法支持。"},{"pid":"a5db93d69751a7be58cc96011a48c19e67d6665c","tid":761331,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T10:00:53.000Z","msg":"佢係日本定係中國？<br />\n我驚我唔識分"},{"pid":"dde67d244d21f0fa09ea9e4660b354fd68b2802a","tid":761331,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T10:22:53.000Z","msg":"LIP SERVICES<br />\n<br />\n比D實際ACTION啦屌你英國佬"},{"pid":"951e5782b58a9df0bd61500626a1c2fb256b8b1f","tid":761331,"uid":73092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T10:23:47.000Z","msg":"關注到2047<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38069a012824e9c17b94a637aaf648ac8d36d591","tid":761331,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T10:26:36.000Z","msg":"關你春事啦屌你老母<br />\n娶個支那妓女扮中立"},{"pid":"72e40f4036f7e2cb1b241eae66711bdd4aa93249","tid":761331,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T10:34:37.000Z","msg":"大英奶共奶到痴左線"}]}